      "briefTitle": "Efficacy of Helium/Oxygen Compared to Air/Oxygen in Severe Exacerbation of Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD)",
      "officialTitle": "An International Phase III Randomised Trial Comparing in Severe Exacerbations of Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease the Efficacy of Helium/Oxygen Versus Air/Oxygen Administered During Spontaneous Breathing and Intermittent Non-Invasive Ventilation.",
